ight: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">整个流程就三步：</span></p><section style="background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 12px;padding: 24px 20px;margin: 24px;border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><p style="font-size: 10px;color: #9CA3AF;margin: 0 0 4px;text-transform: uppercase;letter-spacing: 2px;font-weight: 600;"><span leaf="">FRAMEWORK</span></p><p style="font-size: 13px;color: #1F2937;margin: 0 0 20px;font-weight: 600;"><span leaf="">AI排版工作流</span></p><svg viewBox="0 0 400 80" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" role="img" aria-label="框架图"><rect x="20" y="20" width="60" height="40" rx="4" fill="#fff" stroke="#1F2937" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><text x="50" y="45" font-size="9" fill="#1F2937" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="600"><tspan leaf="">写作</tspan></text><line x1="83" y1="40" x2="117" y2="40" stroke="#1F2937" stroke-width="1.5"></line><polygon points="117,36 123,40 117,44" fill="#1F2937"></polygon><rect x="120" y="20" width="60" height="40" rx="4" fill="#fff" stroke="#1F2937" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><text x="150" y="45" font-size="9" fill="#1F2937" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="600"><tspan leaf="">Ai排版</tspan></text><line x1="183" y1="40" x2="217" y2="40" stroke="#1F2937" stroke-width="1.5"></line><polygon points="217,36 223,40 217,44" fill="#1F2937"></polygon><rect x="220" y="20" width="60" height="40" rx="4" fill="#fff" stroke="#1F2937" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><text x="250" y="45" font-size="9" fill="#1F2937" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="600"><tspan leaf="">自动上传</tspan></text><line x1="283" y1="40" x2="317" y2="40" stroke="#1F2937" stroke-width="1.5"></line><polygon points="317,36 323,40 317,44" fill="#1F2937"></polygon><rect x="320" y="20" width="60" height="40" rx="4" fill="#DC2626"></rect><text x="350" y="45" font-size="9" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700"><tspan leaf="">检查发布</tspan></text></svg><p style="font-size: 11px;color: #6B7280;margin: 14px 0 0;border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;padding-top: 12px;"><span leaf="">Markdown写作→AI自动转换→一键上传发布&nbsp;</span></p></section><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #FFCDD2 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);padding: 0 4px;border-radius: 2px;font-weight: 600;color: #111827;"><span leaf="">第一步：Markdown写作</span></span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">我还是正常写Markdown，该加粗的地方加粗 `</span><span style="border-bottom: 2px solid #EF4444;font-weight: 600;"><span leaf="">文字</span></span><span leaf="">`，该分段的分段。</span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">专注内容本身，不用管任何排版啊格式啊之类的。</span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #FFCDD2 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);padding: 0 4px;border-radius: 2px;font-weight: 600;color: #111827;"><span leaf="">第二步：AI自动转换</span></span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">运行一个命令，AI自动把Markdown转换成精美的HTML格式（你们看到的这种效果）。</span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">包括：</span></p><section style="margin: 8px 24px;padding: 12px 16px;background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 8px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;gap: 12px;"><span style="width: 6px;height: 6px;background: #DC2626;border-radius: 50%;margin-top: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;"></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">章节标题自动生成序号（01、02、03...）</span></p></section><section style="margin: 8px 24px;padding: 12px 16px;background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 8px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;gap: 12px;"><span style="width: 6px;height: 6px;background: #DC2626;border-radius: 50%;margin-top: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;"></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">关键词自动添加渐变高亮</span></p></section><section style="margin: 8px 24px;padding: 12px 16px;background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 8px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;gap: 12px;"><span style="width: 6px;height: 6px;background: #DC2626;border-radius: 50%;margin-top: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;"></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">_金句_自动添加红色下划线</span></p></section><section style="margin: 8px 24px;padding: 12px 16px;background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 8px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;gap: 12px;"><span style="width: 6px;height: 6px;background: #DC2626;border-radius: 50%;margin-top: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;"></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">复杂流程生成横向步骤卡片</span></p></section><section style="margin: 8px 24px;padding: 12px 16px;background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 8px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;gap: 12px;"><span style="width: 6px;height: 6px;background: #DC2626;border-radius: 50%;margin-top: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;"></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">概念解释生成SVG框架图</span></p></section><section style="margin: 8px 24px;padding: 12px 16px;background: #FAFAFA;border-radius: 8px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;gap: 12px;"><span style="width: 6px;height: 6px;background: #DC2626;border-radius: 50%;margin-top: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;"></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">正反案例生成双栏对比框</span></p></section><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #FFCDD2 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);padding: 0 4px;border-radius: 2px;font-weight: 600;color: #111827;"><span leaf="">第三步：一键上传</span></span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">脚本直接调用微信公众号API，文章自动上传到草稿箱。</span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">我只需要在后台预览一下，修改个别字词，确认无误就能发布。</span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #FFCDD2 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);padding: 0 4px;border-radius: 2px;font-weight: 600;color: #111827;"><span leaf="">全程3分钟。</span></span></p><section style="margin: 40px 24px;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #e5e5e5;"><span leaf=""><br></span></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 20px 0;"><span leaf=""><img alt="Image" class="rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder" data-aistatus="1" data-cropx2="832" data-cropy1="194.800875273523" data-cropy2="1039.5448577680527" data-ratio="0.5074074074074074" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Dn2ibXh80Z9BL9DQC4ULMOVZW7WJBAugicObUrPg6HlVwVSNicEGsUsIHJDjHPJtic3xVFbXcolv79SSpQsibw2Oy2w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=2" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; flex-basis: auto; background-color: transparent; aspect-ratio: calc(1.9708) / 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 243.719px !important; height: auto !important;" type="block" data-original-style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;height: auto !important;width: 243.719px !important;visibility: visible !important;" data-index="8" src="