></span><p style="font-size: 14px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0;"><span leaf="">底部互动区（点赞/推荐/分享）</span></p></section><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">写文章时只需要插入特定标记，就能自动触发对应组件。</span></p><section style="margin: 40px 24px;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #e5e5e5;"><span leaf=""><br></span></section></section><section data-mpa-template="t" mpa-data-temp-power-by="yiban.io" mpa-data-temp-type="title" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;justify-content: flex-start;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;align-self: flex-start;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 36px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);line-height: 40px;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section mpa-content-none="t" mpa-from-tpl="t"><span leaf="">06</span><span leaf=""><br></span></section></section><section nodeleaf="" style="width: 13px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin-left: 4px;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><img data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Eqoz7VLNtTX2eJQUCvHjRJF21kHiabYC511N2guUDIbRXWNX7uwA2D41nN7dMIHXw2jYOQOwSxjibRxGsr7XPRQg/640?from=appmsg#imgIndex=11" class="rich_pages wxw-img wx_img_placeholder_mini" data-ratio="2" data-w="26" style="display: block; background-color: transparent; aspect-ratio: calc(0.5) / 1; width: 13px !important; height: auto !important;" data-aistatus="1" data-original-style="display: block;background-color: transparent;" data-index="13" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3