ter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #FFCDD2 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);padding: 0 4px;border-radius: 2px;font-weight: 600;color: #111827;"><span leaf="">投资时间而不是堆砌工具</span></span></p><p style="font-size: 15px;color: #374151;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 0.5px;margin: 0 24px 20px;"><span leaf="">花10小时建一个自动化流程，以后每次省1小时。这笔账怎么算都值。</span></p><section style="margin: 40px 24px;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #e5e5e5;"><span leaf=""><br></span></section></section><section data-mpa-template="t" mpa-data-temp-power-by="yiban.io" mpa-data-temp-type="title" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;justify-content: flex-start;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;align-self: flex-start;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 36px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);line-height: 40px;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><section mpa-content-none="t" mpa-from-tpl="t"><span leaf="">07</span><span leaf=""><br></span></section></section><section nodeleaf="" style="width: 13px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin-left: 4px;" mpa-from-tpl="t"><img data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Eqoz7VLNtTX2eJQUCvHjRJF21kHiabYC511N2guUDIbRXWNX7uwA2D41nN7dMIHXw2jYOQOwSxjibRxGsr7XPRQg/640?from=appmsg#imgIndex=12" class="rich_pages wxw-img wx_img_placeholder_mini" data-ratio="2" data-w="26" style="display: block; background-color: transparent; aspect-ratio: calc(0.5) / 1; width: 13px !important; height: auto !important;" data-aistatus="1" data-original-style="display: block;background-color: transparent;" data-index="14" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg 